### Features
- Next.js 15 + App Router + TypeScript
- Cosmic animated logo with rainbow comet particles (60 fps)
- Lenis smooth scrolling
- Framer Motion animations
- MDX case studies
- 100 Lighthouse scores
- Deployed on Vercel

